parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
RPMs jump or surge
the transmission slips or jerks
the vehicle fails to accelerate
the check engine light is illuminated
and the transmission fails to shift gears properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle are not protected from the impact.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
passenger airbag light stays on even when occupied by an adult
airbag failure to deploy in a frontal collision
airbag failure to deploy in a rollover accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag sensor can lead to the airbag failing to deploy in a crash, or deploying unnecessarily, which can cause injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Passenger airbag light stays on even when occupied by an adult
airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
airbag sensor malfunction
airbag failure to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The recall of the Takata airbag can lead to the airbag failing to deploy in a crash, or deploying unnecessarily, which can cause injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Receipt of recall notification
airbag failure to deploy in a crash
airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or jerks
the vehicle hesitates or stalls
the transmission fails to engage gears
the vehicle vibrates or shakes excessively
the transmission warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the moonroof can cause glass shattering, injuring occupants and obstructing the driver's view, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The moonroof suddenly shatters or explodes
causing glass to fall into the vehicle
and potentially obstructing the driver's view.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels spongy or soft
the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual
the brake warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning gas gauge can cause the driver to run out of fuel, leading to accidents or stranding.
symptoms: The gas gauge does not accurately display the fuel level
the fuel level fluctuates erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or shuts off while driving
the vehicle hesitates or loses power
the engine warning light illuminates.
